<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Solitaire_(cipher)" title="Solitaire (cipher)">Solitaire</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Phelix" title="Phelix">Phelix</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Phelix#Helix" title="Phelix">Helix</a></li>
</ul>
<p><br /></p>
<p><a href="/wiki/Pseudo-random_number_generator" title="Pseudo-random number generator" class="mw-redirect">Pseudo-random number generators</a>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Fortuna_(PRNG)" title="Fortuna (PRNG)">Fortuna</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Yarrow_algorithm" title="Yarrow algorithm">Yarrow algorithm</a></li>
</ul>
<p><a href="/wiki/Block_ciphers" title="Block ciphers" class="mw-redirect">Block ciphers</a>:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Blowfish_(cipher)" title="Blowfish (cipher)">Blowfish</a></li>
